# Follow AGENTS.md

At the start of non-trivial work, treat **`AGENTS.md`** (repo root) as mandatory process.

1. Use `docs/README.md` to choose the SPEC.
2. Apply `docs/PATTERNS_*` instead of inventing UI/code style.
3. Sync `docs/SPEC_*` / `AMENDMENTS.md` after behaviour changes (see `docs-sync` rule).
4. Obey hard constraints in `.claude/CLAUDE.md` and `AGENTS.md` (auth, **DB-first: never invent columns/tables/migrations/schema scripts**, **Mollie mock until client keys**, Azure, store price/login, **owner-only commit/publish**).

Do not ask the user to restate these defaults unless a requirement genuinely conflicts with a SPEC.
